author: arkurth
msg: Added subroutines to Linux.pm: execute, file_exists, delete_file, move_file, copy_file, copy_file_to, copy_file_from, get_file_contents, get_available_space, get_file_size, find_files. These are called by the new VMware code to act on the VM host.
Renamed filesystem_entry_exists to file_exists subroutine in Linux.pm to match other OS modules.
Added escape_file_path, normalize_file_path, and parent_directory_path subroutines to utils.pm. They format file paths and are called by the new subs in Linux.pm.
